headline: How Upward Earnings Estimate Revisions at TE Connectivity (TEL) Have Changed Its Investment Story
summary: In recent days, TE Connectivity has attracted positive analyst attention due to upward revisions in earnings estimates and a recognized momentum in its business fundamentals, placing it among stocks favored by investors focused on robust financial performance metrics. headline: Where Does PLDT Stand After Recovering 0.9% This Week?
summary: Thinking about what to do with your PLDT shares, or considering jumping in? You are definitely not alone. This telco giant has been a mainstay of the Philippine exchange for years, and lately, its price has been anything but boring. In just the past week, PLDT nudged up 0.9%, a small but notable gain, especially after a year that has seen the stock lose more than 20% of its value. Over the last three years, PLDT is close to flat, essentially back to where it started, but zoom out a bit...
